item.title: CVE-2020-9518|2024-08-04T10:34:39.574Z -- micro%20focus%20international -- service%20manager%20%28web%20tier%29.
item.description: Login filter can access configuration files vulnerability in Micro Focus Service Manager (Web Tier), affecting versions 9.50, 9.51, 9.52, 9.60, 9.61, 9.62. The vulnerability could be exploited to allow unauthorized access to configuration data.
